        <abstract>
            <p>Asks whether offspring of cross between African pig and common pig are fertile. Are Lord Rowland Hill’s African pigs domesticated?</p>
            <p>Mentions pigeons’ skeletons.</p> 
<p>Is working at a book on variation [<hi rend="italic">Natural selection</hi>].</p> 
